-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616242\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tzo1665702646556.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tzo1665702646556.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tzo1665702646556.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tzo1665702646556\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Number of units that are displayed between two major ticks. The default is <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">5</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__p_d105674e1_d105675e1_d105676e1\">MinorTickUnits<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__section_or1_rxc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d391109e61\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__section_dtc_sxc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d391109e107\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__p_d105683e1_d105684e1_d105685e1\">For example, in the Meter widget, the default range is\n        set from 0-100. When <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Minor Tick Units</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">5</code>,\n        there are 4 ticks between the annotated tick marks.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__fig_d105686e1_d105687e1_d105688e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Meter Widget with Default Values</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Meter Widget with default values\" class=\"image\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__image_nzs_5xc_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/meterticksdefault.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__section_hmh_vxc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d391109e134\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__pre_g1w_xxc_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"MajorTickUnits=10<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>MinorTickUnits=2\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__fig_d105695e1_d105696e1_d105697e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Meter Widget</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Meter widget\" class=\"image\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__image_wqg_zxc_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/meterticks2.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__section_w4w_zxc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d391109e158\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__ul_kp2_byc_zwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__li_d41993e1_d41994e1_d41995e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bwv1665702644903.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702644903.html\" title=\"The umeter widget displays the value of a Numeric field on a gauge for which there is a predefined range of values marked around the outer edge. Uniface provides a logical widget called Meter, which is mapped to umeter.\">umeter (Meter)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tzo1665702646556__li_d41996e1_d41997e1_d41998e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"foe1665702651174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/foe1665702651174.html\" title=\"The uslider widget allows users to edit a numeric value in a field by sliding an indicator in a set of a previously defined range of values. Uniface provides a logical widget called Slider, which is mapped to uslider.\">uslider (Slider)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616242\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616242\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Minor Tick Units ( MinorTickUnits) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Number of units that are displayed between two major ticks. The default is 5 . MinorTickUnits = Number Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description For example, in the Meter widget, the default range is set from 0-100. When Minor Tick Units is set to 5 , there are 4 ticks between the annotated tick marks. Figure 1. Meter Widget with Default Values Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"MajorTickUnits=10 ; MinorTickUnits=2\" Copy Figure 2. Meter Widget Applies To umeter (Meter) uslider (Slider) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}